.TH "nvme_scan_ctrl" 9 "nvme_scan_ctrl" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_scan_ctrl \- Scan on a controller
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvme_scan_ctrl
.BI "(struct nvme_global_ctx *ctx "  ","
.BI "const char *name "  ","
.BI "nvme_ctrl_t *c "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
struct nvme_global_ctx object
.IP "name" 12
Name of the controller
.IP "c" 12
\fInvme_ctrl_t\fP object to return
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Scans a controller with sysfs name \fIname\fP and add it to \fIr\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or negative error code otherwise
